title_bed_bats_review: Rental unit in Dhaka · ★4.50 · 2 bedrooms · 2 baths
listing_description: Warm apartment ideal for business trip, families or couple. It is very cozy and comfortable space, fully designed and furnished. The apartment includes spacious kitchen, a separate toilet at the entrance of apartment, a cozy bedroom with a nice bathroom and another bedroom and lovely living room. The kitchenette includes small fridge, stove and all necessary cutlery to prepare and enjoy your food. It is always clean, disinfected for the guests to enjoy their stay and to feel comfortable.

You can start your day with a refreshing shower or wind down in the evening with a relaxing cold or hot water bath. A refrigerator is at your disposal. You can start the day with a cup of coffee from the in-room coffee station.
